              "content": "=You are a professional email assistant.\n\nAnalyze this email and respond with:\n1. Category (choose one): Job Opportunity, Customer Support, Spam, Urgent, General Inquiry\n2. Priority (choose one): High, Medium, Low\n3. A professional reply to this email\n\nEmail From: {{ $json.From }}\nEmail Subject: {{ $json.Subject }}\nEmail Content: {{ $json.snippet }}\n\nRespond in this exact format:\nCategory: [category]\nPriority: [priority]\nReply: [your professional reply]"
